prodNameC: "西門子" ACS: 180 去氧比林二酚胺試劑組
ingredientsDesc:
(1) ACS: 180 DPD: lite reagent, solid phase
lite reagent: monoclonal mouse anti-DPD antibody (~450 ng/vial) and polyclonal goat anti-mouse antibody (~195 ng/vial) labeled with acridinium ester in buffered saline with sodium azide (<0.1%) and preservatives.
solid phase: pyridinoline (~0.6 ug/vial) conjucated to avidin (~20 ug/vial) coupled to paramagnetic particels in buffered saline with sodium azide(<0.1%) and preservatives.
(2) DPD 1,2,3 quality control material: after reconstitutuion, various levels of deoxypyridinoline in buffer with sodium chloride and preservatives.
(3) DPD Calibrator: after reconstitution, low or high levels of deoxypyridinoline in buffer with sodium chloride and preservatives.
applicantAddr: 台北市南港區園區街３號８樓
efficacy: 配合"拜耳"全自動冷光免疫分析系統，檢測尿液中去氧比林二酚胺(deoxypyridinoline)。
mdFormat: (1) ACS: 180 DPD (300 tests, 50 tests). (2) DPD 1,2,3 quality control material (2 mL/vial).(3) DPD Calibrator (2mL/vial).
